## THE BUSINESS\
\
### Core Thesis\
\
**AI handles 70% of the work. Humans drive 100% of the change.**\
\
This platform uses AI to orchestrate structured peer accountability groups (squads) at scale. The AI does the matching, facilitation, coaching, tracking, nudging, and sprint management. But the mechanism that actually drives behavior change is human peer accountability \'97 real people who know your goals and will ask you what happened.\
\
The research is clear:\
- Solo goal-setting: 43% completion rate (Dominican University, Dr. Gail Matthews)\
- Written goals shared with accountability partner + weekly reports: 76% completion rate\
- Scheduled accountability appointments with a committed partner: up to 95% (ASTD)\
- No AI-only coaching product has demonstrated results anywhere near these numbers\
\
The insight: Human-led accountability groups work but don't scale (capped by facilitator time and cost). AI solves the scaling problem without replacing the mechanism that works. This is NOT an AI coaching app. This is NOT a community platform. It is an AI-powered engine that makes structured human peer accountability groups work at thousands of concurrent squads \'97 without human facilitators.\
\
### The Product\
\
**Sprint-based peer accountability squads, orchestrated entirely by AI.**\
\
- Members are matched into squads of 6\'968 peers using an AI matching algorithm (timezone, goal type, personality balance, experience level)\
- Each squad runs a 6-week structured sprint:\
  - **Monday:** Goal declaration \'97 each member commits to specific, measurable weekly goals\
  - **Wednesday:** Mid-week check-in \'97 Green/Yellow/Red status, surface blockers, squad support\
  - **Friday:** Reflection & celebration \'97 wins, learnings, adjustments, no shame\
  - **Week 3:** "Dip Intervention" \'97 motivation reset, goal adjustment amnesty\
  - **Week 6:** Retrospective + squad continuation vote (>75% yes = squad stays together)\
- AI agents handle all facilitation, prompting, tracking, progress analytics, and re-engagement\
- A personal AI coach is available 24/7 between human touchpoints for goal refinement, obstacle analysis, and personalized insights\
- The "Pause Protocol" allows struggling members to pause without losing their squad spot (targeting 70% re-engagement vs. 15% with hard cancellation)\
\
